{"tid":1863763,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"原封不動好好長大的Red Velvet澀琪！ 母胎美女鑒定完畢","createTime":"2020-02-05T09:37:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T04:58:48.000Z","uid":16659,"like":23,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"276863a4bbbf3f047c496748d276b61a279c198a","tid":1863763,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T09:37:20.000Z","msg":"照片幾乎涵蓋了澀琪成長全過程，從軟糯的幼兒時期到萌萌的兒童期，再到淑女氣質逐漸養成的學生時期，看完只想說澀琪絕對是母胎美女，純天然。幼兒時的澀琪小臉肉呼呼的，明明桌子上擺著錢和美食，但大眼睛一直盯著生日蛋糕。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_d65c9825978a6fac02bf086c8ef0ac00/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-02-05/124000-812277.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_d65c9825978a6fac02bf086c8ef0ac00%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-02-05%2F124000-812277.png&h=2e3852c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上了幼稚園的澀琪五官逐漸長開，不變的依舊是小肉臉，讓人看了忍不住想要捏一把。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_b5b00a5b4af2d22c9ab702b53d7a3443/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-02-05/124000-812276.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_b5b00a5b4af2d22c9ab702b53d7a3443%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-02-05%2F124000-812276.png&h=5338648d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_16e72880c827f4631f233d8a10fbdabf/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-02-05/124000-812289.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_16e72880c827f4631f233d8a10fbdabf%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-02-05%2F124000-812289.png&h=876c2d23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n隨著慢慢長大，澀琪的嬰兒肥也慢慢消去。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_63b5e1024f30990ce4e9f9f4f84d6508/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-02-05/124000-812275.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_63b5e1024f30990ce4e9f9f4f84d6508%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-02-05%2F124000-812275.png&h=c2c7e223&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上學之後的澀琪氣質漸顯，長髮飄飄，五官精緻，竟然有90年代清純港星的味道。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_cb1cd759aa6922eab834c5c8fd9cc410/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-02-05/124000-812281.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_cb1cd759aa6922eab834c5c8fd9cc410%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-02-05%2F124000-812281.png&h=19d784d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_5ed10b8da7cc8d740abff1c377cc799d/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-02-05/124000-812283.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_5ed10b8da7cc8d740abff1c377cc799d%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-02-05%2F124000-812283.png&h=df9535e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n出道之後的澀琪那肯定是更加精緻了，可鹽可甜，隨時隨地都有一種偶像劇女主角的感覺。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/124000\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.koreastardaily.com%2Ftc%2Fnews%2F124000&d=%2FE8yPsxO6SBEJdrny20pcYaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=631bbfcd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/124000</a>"},{"pid":"f3e13c41dbf647f5110e04cdbdd9553dc8a887a3","tid":1863763,"uid":16659,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T09:39:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唾涎欲滴令人動心 MA-MA-MA-MA-MIA<br />\n勾起一些感覺 MA-MA-MA-MA-MIA<br />\n甜甜蜜蜜在乎內心 試過試過這美味 整整一生都會牽掛</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/759a5425a5884537821098486b3577d4/1b025b67d3b13c4d-dc/s500x750/744d83a50da64b169988e21155287cb23def9ab9.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F759a5425a5884537821098486b3577d4%2F1b025b67d3b13c4d-dc%2Fs500x750%2F744d83a50da64b169988e21155287cb23def9ab9.gifv&h=7b5fd155&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/5b3b092fe074163b2b5c2bd986662a56/1b025b67d3b13c4d-20/s500x750/f56be7884ad7e9871a51edb72c5a925beeba2318.gi